tionality of the\ncMFP will enable it to be adapted as a standard tool in research, development\nand diagnostic laboratories, particularly for the interaction with tissues and\ncells.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Aug 2014 09:51:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-19"}
